The paper deals with the problem of phase retrieval, which is a fundamental problem in signal processing and imaging. The formulation of the problem as a convex optimization problem and the use of Basis Pursuit as the dual problem suggest that the paper is likely to belong to the Information Theory (cs.IT), Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition (cs.CV), Machine Learning (cs.LG), Numerical Analysis (cs.NA), and Signal and Image Processing (cs.SI) sub-categories.
